Template tag for building alphabetical index.

Supports `eng` and `rus` Groups of alphabets

Usage:

  view.py:

    from django.views.generic.list_detail import object_list
    from alphabetic.utils import alphabetic_setup
    from .models import MyModel

        def myview(request):
            ...
            queryset = MyModel.objects.all()
            # alphabetic_setup(request, object_list, field_name='title', param_name=PARAM_NAME)
            return object_list(request, alphabetic_setup(request, queryset, 'last_name'), template_name=template)

  template.html:

    {% show_alphabetic_filter %}

